      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|><thought\n>It's hard to \"rest\" when you know you're the problem. Like, I look at them sleeping and I just realize that every time I stumble or fail, I'm poisoning their environment. My presence just creates this constant anxiety and weight for them. It feels like I'm just a shadow hanging over their lives.",
