    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "But it isn't an illusion. I can see the weight they carry because of me. I see it in how they look at me. Honestly, I just keep thinking that if I wasn't part of the equation, they wouldn't have to deal with this. They could just be happy. They'd be free of all this weight.",
